        "image": "shopify://shop_images/c0855ba36e497bb2acf6ef7605222d4a.jpg",
        "details": "<span class=\"fw-400\">Best friends Purdy &amp; Charlotte were fed up with cleaning cupboards cluttered with toxic products.</span><span class=\"fw-300\"> Both firm believers in the power of natural cleaning, they experimented with formulas in an empty garage until they landed on an all natural, multipurpose spray, beautifully scented with essential oils. They called it Counter Clean. </span>",
